lead_paragraph: In the weeks since Hillary Clinton's shock election defeat to U.S. President-elect Donald Trump, a rumor has taken hold among New York City's political chattering class: could she challenge Mayor Bill de Blasio's reelection bid this year?

headline.main: Hillary Clinton for NYC Mayor? Probably Not, but Rumors Persist
